.. _borg_serve:

borg serve
----------
::

    borg serve <options>

optional arguments
    ``--restrict-to-path PATH``
        | restrict repository access to PATH.  Can be
        | specified multiple times to allow the client
        | access to several directories.

`Common options`_
    |

Description
~~~~~~~~~~~

This command starts a repository server process. This command is usually not used manually.
